    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fazzija: Kails etmu\nes no fawas Mahtes Meeſahu\nnahzis/ un kails es atkat us tur-\nren aiseefchu. Tas KUNGS\nirr Dewis/ tas KUNGS irr neh-\nnis/ lai ta KUNGA Wahrs\nirr flawehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiffas ichunis Leetas\nIjabs ne grehkoja/ un ne turre-\njuhs aplam prett Deewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta II. Nodalla.\nTas Satans us Deewa Palaischanu mekle J.\njabu wehl jo wairak mohziht: 1. Un moḥ,\nzi Ijabu pee fawahm Meeſahm ar nikneem\nAugoneem: 7. Pahrfo winna Geewa win,\nnu apmehd: 9. Ko wiꞥſch tomehr ar Pa-\nzeefchanu paneſs: 10. Trihs Draugi Ijaba\nnahk pee winna/ winnu eepreezinaht: 11.\nUn rauda ar winnu feptinas Deenas/ un\nfeptinas Naftis: 12.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N tas notifke atkat kah-\nda Deenā/ kad tee Dee-\nwa Behrui nahze preekfcb\nta KUNGA stahweht/ tad at-\nnahze arridsan tas Satans wiṫ-\nnu Starpā/ ka tas ta KUNGA\nPreekfcha stahwetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija\nus to Satanu: No kurrenes tu\nnahz? un tas Satans atbildeja\ntau KUNGAM/ un fazzija:\nEs efmu to Semmi zauri isstai-\ngajs/ un ceſtch tahs apkahrt\ngahjis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "us to Satanu: Woj tu ne\nmannu Kalpu Ijabu wehra\nzie? jo ne weens irr tai Sem-\ntahds ka wiꞥſch/ weens ska-\nfirdigs/ un taifs deewabthji\nWihrs/ un atstahjahs no Taun\nun wiꞥſch turrabs wehl stipri\nfawas Sirde-Skaidribas/ bet\neſti manni prett winnu skub-\nnajs wiꞥſchu welti famaitaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Satans ta\nKUNGAM/ un fazzija: Ah-\nprett Ahdu/ un wiſs/ kas Zilu\nkan peederr/ to dohd wiꞥſch p\nfawu Dshwibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet issteep jelle tat\nRohfu/ un atskar winna Ka-\nlus un winna Meetas/ gaun\ndsefi/ ka wiꞥſch tewi Wai-\nlahdehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazz\nus to Satanu: Redst/ lai win-\nirr tawā Rohkā/ touehr tau-\nwinna Dshwibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad isgahje tas Sata-\nno ta KUNGA Preekchas/ i-\ntitte Ijabu ar nikneem Aug-\nneim/ no winna Pehdas lib-\nwinna Galwas Wirsum.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija winna Seen-\nus winnu: Woj tu wehl stip-\nturrecs pee tawas Sirde-Ska-\nribas? lahdi Deewu/ un mirsti\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nehme weer\nPohda Gabbalu/ ka wiꞥſch\nto kazfitohs/ jo wiꞥſch bij apfe-\ndees eeksch Belneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet wiꞥſch fazzija u-\ntahs: Tu runnata ka dascha N-\nnojehga runna/ gribvam mel\n"
    }
  ],
